\c 29
\s Jobho anorangarira mazuva ekufara kwake
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapfuurazve nedimikira rake ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Haiwa, dai ndaiva \add se\add*pamwedzi yekare, sepamazuva Mwari akandichengetedza.
\v 3 Panenge mwenje wake wavhenekera pamusoro wangu, nechiedza chake ndakafamba \add mu\add*rima.
\v 4 Sezvandaiva pamazuva ekuibva kwangu, zano raMwari paraiva pamusoro petende rangu.
\v 5 Wemasimbaose paaiva a\add chiri\add* neni, nevana vangu vakandipoteredza.
\v 6 Pandaisuka matsimba angu neruomba, uye ibwe richidururira nzizi dzemafuta!
\v 7 Pandaibuda kuenda kusuwo nemuguta, ndakagadzira chigaro changu padare.
\v 8 Majaya akandiona ndokuvanda, nevatana vakasimuka vakamira.
\v 9 Machinda akarega kutaura, ndokuisa ruoko pamuromo wawo.
\v 10 Inzwi revakuru rakavanda, nerurimi rwavo rwakanamatira kumusoro kwemumikanwa wavo.
\v 11 Nzeve payainzwa, ndokunditi ndakaropafadzwa, neziso rakaona rikandipupurira.
\v 12 Nokuti ndainunura murombo anochema, nenherera, neasina mubatsiri.
\v 13 Ropafadzo yewotandadza yakawira pamusoro pangu, uye ndakaita moyo wechirikadzi uimbe nemufaro.
\v 14 Ndapfeka kururama, naiko kwakandifukidza; kururamiswa kwangu kwakava senguvo nekorona.
\v 15 Ndaiva meso kumapofu, nuye ndaiva tsoka kumhetamakumbo.
\v 16 Ndaiva baba kune vanoshaiwa; nenyaya yandisingazivi ndakainzvera.
\v 17 Ndakavhuna mazino ewakaipa, nekubvuta chaakajimba kubva pameno ake.
\v 18 Zvino ndakati: Ndichapere nedendere rangu, ndipamhidzire mazuva angu sejecha.
\v 19 Mudzi wangu wakatanda kusvika kumvura, nedova rinorara usiku hwese padavi rangu.
\v 20 Rukudzo rwangu rwutsva mandiri neuta hwangu muruoko rwangu hunovandudzwa.
\v 21 Kwandiri vakateerera, ndokumirira, ndokunyarara pazano rangu.
\v 22 Shure kweshoko rangu havana kushandura, nenhau yangu yakadonhera pamusoro pavo.
\v 23 Uye vakandimirira semvura, uye uromo wavo vakaushamisira kwazvo mvura yekupedzisira.
\v 24 \add Pa\add*ndakavaseka, havana kutenda, nechiedza chechiso changu havana kuwisira pasi.
\v 25 Ndaka\add va\add*sarudzira nzira yavoi, ndokugara samambo pakati pehondo yakarongwa, seanonyaradza vanochema.
